  "name": "Morrison COU1 — CPB hemolysis credibility assessment (W-ON-02 adversarial)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under cardiopulmonary bypass (CPB) conditions. COU1 evaluates whether the computational model can identify worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for a Class II CPB device at Model Risk Level 2. Full 13-factor assessment: 7 factors assessed (all meeting required levels), 6 factors not assessed (acceptable at MRL 2). This package intentionally omits hasApplicabilityConstraint and hasOperatingEnvelope from the ContextOfUse, triggering W-ON-02.",
  "bindsRequirement": "https://uofa.net/synth/req/morrison-cpb-hemolysis-req",
  "bindsClaim": "https://uofa.net/synth/claim/morrison-cpb-hemolysis-claim",
  "bindsModel": "https://uofa.net/synth/model/morrison-cfd-hemolysis-model",
