      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Solver must demonstrate correct numerical implementation via benchmark problems at Gradation 1 or higher.",
      "rationale": "ANSYS Fluent has been verified against standard CFD benchmark cases including lid-driven cavity and backward-facing step. Vendor-supplied verification documentation reviewed and deemed adequate for MRL 2."
    },
    {
