      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Mesh convergence study required demonstrating discretization error below 5% for primary QoI (hemolysis index) at Gradation 2.",
      "rationale": "A three-level mesh refinement study was performed (coarse: 2.1M cells, medium: 5.8M cells, fine: 14.3M cells). Grid Convergence Index (GCI) for hemolysis index was 2.1% between medium and fine meshes. Medium mesh selected for production runs. Achieved Gradation 3 exceeds required Gradation 2."
    },
